The '''Mhingxin''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Rodent/Legends|rodent]]-faced [[Sentience/Legends|sentients]] with a reputation for high-pitched voices. They tended to have a low opinion of themselves, since their appearance was similar to the sewer rats and such scum that beings all over [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] despised, hated, and strived to exterminate. They were easily provoked because of this. [[Eobbim Figh]] was a male Mhingxin.

